id: pm-d97r
title: Single-source Codex plugin docs tool surface
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: Codex plugin docs repeat install/tool-surface text with hand-maintained action lists in docs/CODEX_PLUGIN.md:13-33 and plugins/pm-codex/README.md:3-33. Both describe what the plugin provides, install steps, MCP launcher fallback, narrow tools, pm_run actions, and safety guidance, but docs/CODEX_PLUGIN.md:16-17 and plugins/pm-codex/README.md:24-26 differ in named tools/actions. Existing pm-js0r is implementation wrapper/smoke dedup and pm-rjgh does not cover Codex plugin docs."
